</p>
<p>Now, if the <code>fetchAllShipsData()</code> method throws an exception, the page will <em>not</em> die.
Instead, the code inside <code>catch</code> will be called and then execution will keep going like normal:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="7dccd14a6b">
